data.description: Welcome to  713 N Ashland  Ave. This charming 2 bedroom one bath home comes with almost a whole acre of land! The cozy kitchen has a nice view of the yard and imagine morning coffee or tea while enjoying the view from the front porch. The dining room is great for those family dinners or convert it to an office, craft room, whatever you need! The living room and bedrooms are roomy with lots of closet space. Newer furnace, hot water tank and home warranty will add to your peace of mind. Make 713 N Ashland yours today!
